PrEP i̲s̲ efficacious for HIV-1 prevention among women 𝓊𝓈𝒾𝓃𝑔 DMPA and men w͎h͎o͎s͎e͎ partners use DMPA ,̴ suggesting PrEP 𝗰𝗼𝘂𝗹𝗱 mitigate the potential ɪɴᴄʀᴇᴀꜱᴇᴅ HIV-1 a̴c̴q̴u̴i̴s̴i̴t̴i̴o̴n̴ and transmission risks that 𝐡𝐚𝐯𝐞 b͓̽e͓̽e͓̽n͓̽ 𝙖𝙨𝙨𝙤𝙘𝙞𝙖𝙩𝙚𝙙 with 𝙳𝙼𝙿𝙰 use.

PrEP 𝔦𝔰 ᴇꜰꜰɪᴄᴀᴄɪᴏᴜꜱ 𝔣𝔬𝔯 H̳I̳V̳-1 prevention among women 𝔲𝔰𝔦𝔫𝔤 𝑫𝑴𝑷𝑨 and men whose partners use DMPA, 𝒔𝒖𝒈𝒈𝒆𝒔𝒕𝒊𝒏𝒈 PrEP could mitigate the potential increased H̲I̲V̲-1͓̽ acquisition 𝘢𝘯𝘥 transmission risks that have been associated with DMPA use.

𝘗𝘳𝘌𝘗 is efficacious for HIV-1 p͎r͎e͎v͎e͎n͎t͎i͎o͎n͎ among 𝕨𝕠𝕞𝕖𝕟 using DMPA a̷n̷d̷ 𝗺𝗲𝗻 whose partners use 𝘋𝘔𝘗𝘈 ,̾ suggesting PrEP could mitigate the potential i͓̽n͓̽c͓̽r͓̽e͓̽a͓̽s͓̽e͓̽d͓̽ HIV-1̳ acquisition and transmission risks that have 𝓫𝓮𝓮𝓷 a̳s̳s̳o̳c̳i̳a̳t̳e̳d̳ with DMPA use.

P̴r̴E̴P̴ is efficacious for H̶I̶V̶-1 prevention among women 𝕦𝕤𝕚𝕟𝕘 DMPA a̶n̶d̶ men whose partners use D͎M͎P͎A͎, suggesting PrEP c̳o̳u̳l̳d̳ mitigate the potential i̷n̷c̷r̷e̷a̷s̷e̷d̷ H̶I̶V̶-1 𝐚𝐜𝐪𝐮𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝒶𝓃𝒹 transmission risks that have been associated w̾i̾t̾h̾ DMPA use.
